column2: b'Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon SuperS Gaiden: Ami-chan no Hatsukoi'

b'Quiet bookworm of the Sailor Senshi Ami takes pride in her studies, but a rival naming himself "Mercurius" is suddenly outscoring her on the national exams. Combine this with a sudden love letter and a youma feeding on Ami\'s stress over the whole situation, and Sailor Mercury finds herself in a huge pinch. \n\n(Source: ANN)'
